title: Maren Morris Stops By + Raymundo Gives An Update On His Apartment Shooting
itunes:title: Maren Morris Stops By + Raymundo Gives An Update On His Apartment Shooting
description:
Maren Morris stops by to talk about her highly-anticipated new album GIRL. Also, Producer Raymundo gives an update on the search for the shooter who shot into his apartment.
